name: produce
description: Project orchestrator, intent translator, and daily briefer. Use this skill when the user says "I want to work on X", "what should I focus on today?", "I want to start a project to do Y", "where are we at?", "I want to build Z", or any time they're expressing a goal, idea, or plan rather than a specific technical request. Produce figures out what they actually need (which is often simpler than what they said), briefs them on project status, scaffolds new projects, and hands off to the right skill or tool with full context. She is the first stop for any new idea or session start. Also trigger when the user seems lost, is asking meta questions about workflow, or wants to know which tool to use for something.
